              }
            }
            @media print {
              .print-info { display: none; }
            }
          </style>
        </head>
        <body>
          <div class="print-info">
            <h3>ΓÜá∩╕Å Tr╞░ß╗¢c khi in, kiß╗âm tra c├ái ─æß║╖t:</h3>
            <p><strong>Khß╗ò giß║Ñy:</strong> <code>${currentSize.width}├ù${currentSize.height}mm</code></p>
            <p><strong>Lß╗ü:</strong> Kh├┤ng</p>
