                        Nhß║¡p dß╗» liß╗çu tß╗½ b├¬n ngo├ái
                    </h2>
                    <button
                        onClick={onClose}
                        className="p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 rounded-full transition-colors text-slate-500"
