            // ≡ƒö╣ FIX: Nß║┐u tß║ío phiß║┐u mß╗¢i vß╗¢i paymentStatus = 'paid', gß╗ìi complete_payment ─æß╗â trß╗½ kho
            // Kiß╗âm tra flag inventoryDeducted tß╗½ response cß╗ºa atomic create
            // Nß║┐u atomic create ─æ├ú trß╗½ kho rß╗ôi (inventoryDeducted = true) th├¼ KH├öNG gß╗ìi complete_payment nß╗»a
            if (
              paymentStatus === "paid" &&
              selectedParts.length > 0 &&
              !responseData?.inventoryDeducted
            ) {
              try {
                const result = await completeWorkOrderPayment(
                  orderId,
                  formData.paymentMethod || "cash",
                  0 // Sß╗æ tiß╗ün = 0 v├¼ ─æ├ú thanh to├ín hß║┐t rß╗ôi, chß╗ë cß║ºn trß╗½ kho
                );
                if (!result.ok) {
                  showToast.warning(
                    "─É├ú l╞░u phiß║┐u nh╞░ng c├│ lß╗ùi khi trß╗½ kho: " +
                    (result.error.message || "Lß╗ùi kh├┤ng x├íc ─æß╗ïnh")
                  );
