          <p className="text-xl text-center text-emerald-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Nhß╗»ng c├┤ng viß╗çc bß║úo tr├¼, sß╗¡a chß╗»a chß║Ñt l╞░ß╗úng cß╗ºa ch├║ng t├┤i
